            </p>
            <p>
              <i class="fas fa-phone"></i>
              <a href="tel:+919812345678">+91-9876543210</a>,
              <a href="tel:+919812345678">+91-1122334455</a>
            </p>
            <p>
              <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
              <a
                href="https://mail.google.com/mail/?view=cm&fs=1&to=sudhanshu95084145@gmail.com&su=Hello&body=This%20is%20a%20default%20message"
                target="_blank"
                >info@gvpschool.edu.in</a
              >
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="copy-right">
        <i class="far fa-copyright"></i> 2025 St. Columbus Public School. All
        rights reserved. | Developed by
